room_title: Escape room "The Hotel" by Mission: Escape Atlanta in Atlanta
room_address: 500 Bishop St. Suite E3 Atlanta, GA 30318
room_description: Monsieur Moe's childhood was not an easy one: forced to work at his father's hotel ever since he was little, he became very antisocial and never had any friends. When dad passed away, the Grandjestic Atlantat was signed over to Moe. People who come here once to stay never see the outside world again... Will you be forced to stay here and keep Moe company forever, or will you escape?
